==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|schalowe||not deep, shallow|lang=enm}}; apparently related to {{etyl|ang|-}} {{term|sceald||shallow|lang=ang}}. See also {{l|en|shoal}}.

